A JEALOUS girlfriend who glassed a girl in the face after her boyfriend's complimentary remark has been spared jail. Glass attack woman is spared jail A JEALOUS girlfriend who glassed a girl in the face after her boyfriend's complimentary remark has been spared jail.Lindsay Ross, 26, assaulted Leanne Gray in the Two Heided Man in Hope Street.Ross, from Barmulloch, admitted assault at Glasgow Sheriff Court. She was given a 10-month restriction of liberty order on condition she doesn't leave her house between 8pm and 7am. 